{
  "stem": "7722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 26.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later when he came in the barn, I told him, I am back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in two weeks or three, I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, I want to just tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The instinct in a human being of survival is so strong-- so strong-- I did convince myself that the body creates extra energy, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was laying 16 months in the same clothing and the same underwear.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I was hiding in the barns, not taking a bath-- laying by myself, not to talk to nobody.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] How-- how I am of sound mind-- [CRYING] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't believe [CRYING] I went through, and I could-- and I could do it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had no chance-- no chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know how long Hitler almost got the whole world.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just still the instinct of survival is so strong.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You want to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You want to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't know for different reasons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want to stay alive to tell-- to tell-- to tell the world what they did to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was liberated in 1944, in February.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Soviet Union-- the Soviet army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Soviet army.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of the Jewish people-- all the Jewish-- I mean, all the-- we were about 10 or 15-- that's all from the whole town, who survived.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our town between 4,000 and 5,000 people-- only 10 or 15 people-- we came in one town together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Zdolbunow, what I said before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Over there, we came together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we came-- we came by ourselves-- we came, I don't know how we hired a Ukrainian to-- with the horses.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we came to this town, all the survivors became-- oh, they were-- we were about 10 or 15 people.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
